title: Loituma - Kuutamolla (In the Moonlight)
description:
This is the second album from Loituma, a Finnish group which performs folk music. I couldn&#039;t find a single torrent for this album anywhere, so I figured I ought to upload one. 

I&#039;ve included the album artwork in the folder. 

Note: The Ievan Polka song is not on this album, so don&#039;t download it and then get disappointed when it isn&#039;t there.
